Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好了 不会再一声不吭地远去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何也无法参加你的葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗 就在昨天你还在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时…都在我身边不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 就留下这种信…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是我而是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹…回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说些…说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十九幕\N即使我将不再是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后到F3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王由C7到C6
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐格拉尔银行股似乎连日涨停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士到E4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他投资的股票全都维持高位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈亚那家伙 意外地干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 现在开始卖出他投资的全部股票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎自不用说 东方、王国、边境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各交易所陆续收市之前 不断卖出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卒到C4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海黛说有话想跟您说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱您更甚亲父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法眼睁睁看着您继续转变下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您别再继续这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将骑士从E4移去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的棋子就要毫不留情地舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍我复仇的一切都不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔图乔 把海黛带走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 您仅仅是把我当作复仇的道具才救我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我相信您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 伯爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卒到C5
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看哪 安德烈亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今日股价
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人笑得合不拢嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你才能如此成功 感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 关于与令媛的婚礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说什么友人猝死 无法立即举行婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知像谁 这么顽固不化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 母亲大人的情况如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直卧床不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能前去探望…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 你能去陪她的话一定能让她解解闷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我们银行资产到底能增加到何种程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个都进展顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲打算离开巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回母亲的故乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然生活会比这儿俭朴不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们两人的话 总能想办法糊口…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真会见风使舵 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底都是因为母亲你们才会弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们卷入母亲和爱慕您的男人们无聊的人际关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么偏偏是弗朗兹非死不可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 你去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道 没有目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不在乎任何事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆我也死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想责怪母亲尽管责怪一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请你…请你更加珍惜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「禁止通行」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行证呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有带 平时都可以过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊 老把自己当贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的识别号码已被剥夺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许随便通行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋父亲只能生出笨蛋儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去申请通行证吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是人家肯发给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混帐骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 离我的摩托远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这摩托是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少自以为是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副样子可不适合美丽的您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 反正我总是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到您悲伤的样子 真令人心疼欲裂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人都这样 不过是哄我开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直陪在您身边 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在今天…就在此刻 叫我维多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弗朗兹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在哪轮到你担心别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐 阿尔贝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐 怎么这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么去了 她一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 十六岁生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在大家面前炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些能不能私底下再做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了各位 下面请出本次派对的特别来宾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝在Luna时的恩人—基督山伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让他来巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 不是我们拜托他无论如何都要来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 大家都很想认识伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 他是为了向我们复仇而回巴黎的恶魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您先去和伯爵打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 母亲快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮和弗朗兹也快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 能逃多远逃多远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙您招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 停下 弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是杀害你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「很有趣」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为弗朗兹报仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害我的人 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我是想救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是只考虑自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是总把我的话当耳边风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 弗朗兹 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨你一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹 不要 别死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话一定要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 别从我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 弗朗兹 别死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:13:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿尔贝 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么活蹦乱跳的我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勒诺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然碰上抢了你摩托的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 你的摩托也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏人们收到了惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 工具和机械狂的好友是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过急急忙忙赶到这来 车都成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白我有多期待这一天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找来珍贵的部件 忍了又忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中充满期待 高高兴兴开出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看到你的摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那家伙是谁」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得问个究竟 走上前去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扳手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱车呈现出修复的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比修不好的机器更可怜的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救瓦朗蒂娜那天可惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原来是你的车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 说起那时的痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜都快死了你还在想这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会啊 我是听说要救瓦朗蒂娜才…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是有点喜欢瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可从没说过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 你还记得那天大家一起来这儿兜风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就发生在不久前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却好像已经是遥远的回忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时瓦朗蒂娜分给我们吃的手制点心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无比的美味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 只是想起点…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总被你挂在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我的心灵只能靠机器来抚慰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勒诺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在不断抛售 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已尝试解套 但来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用所有资金买入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但暴跌的不只是银行和集团股
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您投资的所有股票都在暴跌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析不能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析不能？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去我会破产的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有不明病毒入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东方股市也要开盘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法解套所持股票
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银行股以外全部卖出 换成现金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天巴黎天晴 晴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气温22度 晴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降水概率也在10％以下 晴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将是个晴朗的好天气 晴 晴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 振作啊 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东方股市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日的巴黎股市全线急速下跌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 赶快开始处理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐格拉尔集团股由于被大量抛售的影响…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人赶不及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴 晴 晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮 我可爱的女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实已经决定于后天举行你和安德烈亚的婚礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹才刚刚去世 怎么能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的任性让我 不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这一家子横尸街头也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我冷静？开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:18:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,股票暴跌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财产全都浮云了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种廉价的钢琴 给我停止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能救大家的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在立即和安德烈亚结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 只要钱能回来就行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下安德烈亚的财产全都是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮 现在只有你最可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹就在我们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉他在为我们指路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勒诺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚您去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 住手 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵族家的小姐 碰上这种事可真糟蹋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天起你就是我的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主菜得留到那时慢慢品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时何处 你都不是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 岩窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十幕\N再见，欧仁妮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然后期待
